Description_lang: $?a137041[Casting Sundering within $s2 yards of your Surging Totem causes it to create a Tremor at $s1% effectiveness at the target area.][Allies affected by your Earthen Wall Totem, Ancestral Protection Totem, and Earthliving effect receive $457566s1% increased healing from you.]

description_blz.en_US: Allies affected by your Earthen Wall Totem, Ancestral Protection Totem, and Earthliving effect receive 15% increased healing from you.
description_blz.es_MX: Los aliados que estén bajo el efecto de Tótem Muro de tierra, Tótem de protección ancestral y Vida terrestre reciben un 15% más de sanación de tu parte.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aliados sob efeito dos seus Totem de Muralha Terrana, Totem de Proteção Ancestral e Terraviva recebem 15% a mais de cura de você.
description_blz.de_DE: Verbündete, die von Eurem Totem des irdenen Walls, Totem des Schutzes der Ahnen oder Eurem Effekt 'Lebensgeister' betroffen sind, erhalten 15% mehr Heilung von Euch.
description_blz.en_GB: Allies affected by your Earthen Wall Totem, Ancestral Protection Totem, and Earthliving effect receive 15% increased healing from you.
description_blz.es_ES: Los aliados afectados por tu Tótem Muro de tierra, Tótem de Protección ancestral y tu efecto de Vida terrestre reciben un 15% más de sanación de ti.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les personnages alliés affectés par vos effets Totem de mur terrestre, Totem de protection ancestrale ou Viveterre reçoivent 15 % de soins supplémentaires de votre part.
description_blz.it_IT: Gli alleati affetti da un tuo effetto di Totem del Muro Terrigeno, Totem del Risveglio Ancestrale o Terra Benefica ricevono il 15% di cure aggiuntive da te.
description_blz.ru_RU: Вы восполняете на 15% больше здоровья союзникам, на которых действует ваш "Тотем земляной стены", "Тотем защиты Предков" или эффект "Жизнь Земли".
description_blz.ko_KR: 대지의 벽 토템, 선조의 보호 토템, 대지생명 효과에 영향을 받는 아군은 시전자에게 받는 치유 효과가 15%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 盟友受你的大地盾牆圖騰、先祖保護圖騰和大地生命效果影響時，你對其造成的治療效果提高15%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 被你的大地之墙图腾、先祖护佑图腾和大地生命效果影响的盟友受到你的治疗效果提高15%。
